label("$5$", (B + O)/2, NE);
label("$8$", (B + D)/2, S);
label("$x$", (A + C)/2, N);
label("$A$", A, W);
label("$B$", B, E);
label("$C$", C, E);
label("$D$", D, W);
label("$O$", O, N);
[/asy]The answer is in the form k\sqrt{m}+n,. Please provide the value of k + m + n.

Remember to put your answer on its own line after "Answer:".

